code: @Override public void readFrom(StreamInput in) throws IOException {     super.readFrom(in).     shardId = ShardId.readShardId(in).     originalIndices = OriginalIndices.readOriginalIndices(in). }
@Override public void writeTo(StreamOutput out) throws IOException {     super.writeTo(out).     shardId.writeTo(out).     OriginalIndices.writeOriginalIndices(originalIndices, out). }
